data.description: For more information on this property, contact the Listing Agent, Jacque Phelps at (520) 665-4214 or JHP1986@msn.com. This is such a lovely home on a large corner lot. Flooring is Saltillo tile & bedrooms are carpeted. Ceiling fans in all rooms. Closets feature built in shelves for optimal storage. Master bath with large shower & closet space. Hall bath features double sinks & tile counter tops. Laundry room large enough to have extra freezer & or refrigerator, also has large pantry. Kitchen has solid oak cabinets and Corian counter tops. Appliances include dishwasher, trash compactor, oven/stove, refrigerator. Home has an attached 1 car garage with storage and there is also a detached garage that is 1500 sq. ft. It can accommodate 4 large vehicles, a 10 x 10 office with stalled toilet and double shop sink, 10-220 outlets, 20-110 outlets, ample attic storage & evaporative cooler. Heavy gage steel roof.
